New York City Construction Company You Can Rely On

Masonry

Our expert masons transform commercial and residential spaces with high-quality materials and unmatched craftsmanship. Whether you require brickwork, stonework, or concrete services, trust our team to deliver outstanding results. Our comprehensive masonry services include brick and block installations, tuckpointing, retaining walls, and decorative concrete work, ensuring a beautiful and durable result.

Roofing

Your roof is the first line of defense against the elements. Our experienced roofing team ensures that your property is protected with durable, long-lasting roofing systems. From new installations to repairs and maintenance, our general contractor services have got you covered. We specialize in a wide range of roofing materials, including asphalt shingles, metal, slate, and flat roofing systems.

Waterproofing

Water damage can lead to costly repairs and potential health hazards. Our waterproofing solutions provide your building with the best protection against moisture intrusion. Our comprehensive services include foundation waterproofing, exterior wall coatings, and more. Our experts utilize advanced techniques and high-quality materials to ensure a long-lasting waterproofing solution for your property.

Power Washing

Maintain the beauty and cleanliness of your property with our professional power washing services. We utilize state-of-the-art equipment to remove dirt, grime, and mold, restoring your building’s exterior to its original splendor. Our power washing services are perfect for sidewalks, driveways, decks, and building exteriors, providing a deep clean that enhances the aesthetic appeal of your property.

Facade Restoration

Over time, your building’s facade can deteriorate due to weather, pollution, and other factors. Our facade restoration services help preserve the integrity and aesthetic appeal of your property. Our skilled team specializes in brick, stone, and concrete facade restoration, ensuring a stunning transformation that enhances the structural integrity and value of your property.

Painting Services

Water damage can lead to costly repairs and potential health hazards. Our painting solutions provide your building with the best protection against moisture intrusion. Our comprehensive services include interior and exterior painting, utilizing high-quality materials to ensure a long-lasting, professional finish for your property.

Why Choose Brick Tech Contracting Corp?

Experienced and Skilled Team

Our construction company NYC team consists of highly skilled and experienced professionals who are dedicated to providing superior craftsmanship and unparalleled customer service. With a keen eye for detail, we ensure that every project is completed to the highest standards.

We proudly serve clients in Brooklyn, Queens, and the entire New York City area. As your trusted general contractor Brooklyn/Queens provider, we are committed to delivering exceptional services tailored to your specific needs.

Transparent Pricing and Accurate Estimates

We understand that every project is unique, and we provide transparent pricing and accurate estimates to help you make informed decisions. Our commitment to integrity and honesty is the foundation of our long-standing relationships with our clients.

Proven Track Record

With over 30 years of experience in the construction industry, Brick Tech Contracting Corp has built an impeccable reputation for delivering top-quality general contractor New York City services. Our portfolio of successful projects and satisfied clients speaks volumes about our expertise and dedication to excellence.

Fully Licensed and Insured

We are a fully licensed and insured construction company NYC, ensuring your peace of mind and the utmost protection for your investment. We adhere to strict safety guidelines and industry standards, ensuring the highest quality of workmanship on every project.

Customized Solutions

We understand that every project is unique, and we provide customized solutions to meet your specific needs. Our team of experts works closely with you to ensure that your project is completed to your satisfaction.

Timely Project Completion

We are committed to completing your project on time and within budget. Our team of professionals works diligently to ensure that your project is completed to the highest standards.
